{"tid":1152621,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"好心猁迷咁撚柒就縮返入老母個閪度啦","createTime":"2019-05-13T05:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T11:42:55.000Z","uid":174953,"like":70,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a3012e7608e00844830f897c64c4816a2da79d6f","tid":1152621,"uid":174953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:54:31.000Z","msg":"97分亞軍，今季黑哨越位入波，對面龍派膠，馬列斯12碼唔入，可以講真係神秘力量幫緊你地，但你隊柒頭領先7分都可以變輸1分，見住你地由射到滿地精去到最後要係咁反燈，撐死敵獌贏鏝，真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要得你隊柒頭猁次次聖誕節冠軍之後都可以拎唔到冠，你地就預撚左今日就比人指住個柒頭黎笑啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n知你班猁一定搵獌做遮醜布嫁啦，又要係咁開po講資格論，問獌迷有咩資格笑，真係煩撚過閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />獌今季廢到垃圾咁，已經比人笑到面都黃，但至少獌仲有13座英超，相反你地猁狗，踢左十幾年一座英超都無，連降左班既暴力般都指撚緊你地黎笑啦傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995660d5a9314c9eba5f45864a075e4e6491b0ab","tid":1152621,"uid":242630,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:56:09.000Z","msg":"真猁：我地有既係歷史，有既係未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b122a14ba6c4898d3b92c5ef89efacf36a50341b","tid":1152621,"uid":192589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"真係好邪"},{"pid":"99266fe67b98cb103f57ffdd6e840b13ffbf3878","tid":1152621,"uid":174953,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:51:15.000Z","msg":"見到班猁迷柒到咁真係忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d075072668a2626df020547c69dd22799312574b","tid":1152621,"uid":79037,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T06:54:31.000Z","msg":"乜野雖敗猶榮<br />\n乜野值得尊